title: Falacos - Food Truck
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Fast food, Mexican, Catering, Fusion, Take-out only
description: Vegan food truck selling tacos balls which are made of chickpeas, onion, garlic, parsley, and spices. The balls are fried in peanut oil, set in a corn tortilla with hummus creation, fresh vegetables, and sauce. Offers a variety of taco balls flavors and different sauces. Began service in spring 2016. Check its webpage for location changes & updates.
